quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  64,1,Yusabbiĥu Lillāhi Mā Fī As-Samāwāti Wa Mā Fī Al-'Arđi Lahu Al-Mulku Wa Lahu Al-Ĥamdu Wa Huwa `Alá Kulli Shay'in Qadīrun
  64,2,Huwa Al-Ladhī Khalaqakum Faminkum Kāfirun Wa Minkum Mu'uminun Wa Allāhu Bimā Ta`malūna Başīrun
  64,3,Khalaqa As-Samāwāti Wa Al-'Arđa Bil-Ĥaqqi Wa Şawwarakum Fa'aĥsana Şuwarakum Wa 'Ilayhi Al-Maşīru
  64,4,Ya`lamu Mā Fī As-Samāwāti Wa Al-'Arđi Wa Ya`lamu Mā Tusirrūna Wa Mā Tu`linūna Wa Allāhu `Alīmun Bidhāti Aş-Şudūri
  64,5,Alam Ya'tikum Naba'u Al-Ladhīna Kafarū Min Qablu Fadhāqū Wabāla 'Amrihim Wa Lahum `Adhābun 'Alīmun
  64,6,Dhālika Bi'annahu Kānat Ta'tīhim Rusuluhum Bil-Bayyināti Faqālū 'Abasharun Yahdūnanā Fakafarū Wa Tawallaw Wa Astaghná Allāhu Wa Allāhu Ghanīyun Ĥamīdun
  64,7,Za`ama Al-Ladhīna Kafarū 'An Lan Yub`athū Qul Balá Wa Rabbī Latub`athunna Thumma Latunabba'uunna Bimā `Amiltum Wa Dhalika `Alá Allāhi Yasīrun
  64,8,Fa'āminū Billāhi Wa Rasūlihi Wa An-Nūri Al-Ladhī 'Anzalnā Wa Allāhu Bimā Ta`malūna Khabīrun
  64,9,Yawma Yajma`ukum Liyawmi Al-Jam`i Dhālika Yawmu At-Taghābuni Wa Man Yu'umin Billāhi Wa Ya`mal Şāliĥāan Yukaffir `Anhu Sayyi'ātihi Wa Yudkhilhu Jannātin Tajrī Min Taĥtihā Al-'Anhāru Khālidīna Fīhā 'Abadāan Dhālika Al-Fawzu Al-`Ažīmu